{"sgc":false,"sfy":false,"qfy":false,"transUser":{"id":34420906,"status":99,"demand":1,"userid":1645980694,"nickname":"派大-嗨","uptime":1669965024110},"lrc":{"version":27,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Max Elto\"}]}\n{\"t\":780,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Max Elto\"}]}\n[00:01.56]They say that life is always easier,\n[00:05.94]after you let yourself come undone.\n[00:11.56]They say they'll give you all that you want,\n[00:16.63]and I'll be waiting in the shadow of the sun.\n[00:20.46]Seizing time when no one has been before\n[00:24.02]close the curtains what are you waiting for?\n[00:27.63]And I'll be keeping secrets till I'm in the ground.\n[00:50.94]Changing colors makes you waste away,\n[00:54.50]just paint your eyes with a vivid mind.\n[00:58.60]Now you see what's behind the lights,\n[01:02.10]And I'll be waiting in the shadow of the sun.\n[01:06.11]Finding treasures that‘s been on demise,\n[01:09.93]building mountains in disguise,\n[01:13.69]and I'll be keeping secrets till I'm in the ground.\n[01:20.27]I'm in the shadow of the shadow of the sun,\n[01:23.62]where I belong there's something coming on.\n[01:27.71]I'm in the shadow of the shadow of the sun,\n[01:31.91]oh and I need you.\n[01:35.37]I'm in the shadow of the shadow of the sun,\n[01:38.75]where I belong, there's something coming on.\n[01:43.14]No more waiting, times are changing,\n[01:46.90]and there's something coming on.\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":20,"lyric":"[by:派大-嗨]\n[00:01.56]世人常说，世间常易\n[00:05.94]在你自甘堕落之后\n[00:11.56]他们说他们会给你想要的一切\n[00:16.63]而我选择在阴影中期盼阳光\n[00:20.46]试图留住时间\n[00:24.02]拉上窗帘，你还在等什么呢？\n[00:27.63]那永远的秘密也伴随生命消逝\n[00:50.94]改变颜色会让你憔悴\n[00:54.50]只要用生动的思想画出你的眼睛\n[00:58.60]现在你看到灯后面是什么了\n[01:02.10]而我选择在阴影中等待阳光\n[01:06.11]寻找被毁灭的宝藏\n[01:09.93]重山叠嶂将是我竖起的伪装\n[01:13.69]那永存的秘密也将伴随生命消逝\n[01:20.27]活在光下，犹在阴影中\n[01:23.62]属于我的地方发生了一些事情\n[01:27.71]我在太阳的阴影下\n[01:31.91]我需要你\n[01:35.37]我在太阳的阴影下\n[01:38.75]在属于我的地方，发生了一些事情\n[01:43.14]不再等待，时代在变\n[01:46.90]而且有一些事情发生了\n"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"yrc":{"version":32,"lyric":"{\"t\":-1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Max Elto\"}]}\n{\"t\":-500,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Max Elto\"}]}\n[0,5370](0,240,0)They (240,300,0)say (540,270,0)that (810,810,0)life (1620,240,0)is (1860,600,0)always (2460,2550,0)easier(5010,360,0),\n[5370,5490](5370,450,0)after (5820,300,0)you (6120,330,0)let (6450,1200,0)yourself (7650,420,0)come (8070,2730,0)undone(10800,60,0).\n[10860,4980](10860,240,0)They (11100,270,0)say (11370,270,0)they'll (11640,300,0)give (11940,210,0)you (12150,480,0)all (12630,150,0)that (12780,300,0)you (13080,510,0)want(13590,2250,0),\n[15840,3840](15840,300,0)and (16140,180,0)I'll (16320,180,0)be (16500,540,0)waiting (17040,210,0)in (17250,120,0)the (17370,600,0)shadow (17970,180,0)of (18150,120,0)the (18270,1200,0)sun(19470,210,0).\n[19680,3780](19680,630,0)Seizing (20310,330,0)time (20640,180,0)when (20820,240,0)no (21060,120,0)one (21180,90,0)has (21270,240,0)been (21510,1950,0)before\n[23490,3750](23490,450,0)close (23940,120,0)the (24060,570,0)curtains (24630,240,0)what (24870,60,0)are (24930,90,0)you (25020,450,0)waiting (25470,960,0)for(26430,810,0)?\n[27240,22950](27240,330,0)And (27570,180,0)I'll (27750,180,0)be (27930,1500,0)keeping (29430,1740,0)secrets (31170,390,0)till (31560,270,0)I'm (31830,240,0)in (32070,300,0)the (32370,1350,0)ground(33720,16470,0).\n[50190,3600](50190,600,0)Changing (50790,510,0)colors (51300,300,0)makes (51600,150,0)you (51750,360,0)waste (52110,1650,0)away(53760,30,0),\n[53790,4080](53790,360,0)just (54150,270,0)paint (54420,150,0)your (54570,570,0)eyes (55140,270,0)with (55410,150,0)a (55560,450,0)vivid (56010,1590,0)mind(57600,270,0).\n[57870,3630](57870,420,0)Now (58290,60,0)you (58350,480,0)see (58830,330,0)what's (59160,510,0)behind (59670,150,0)the (59820,600,0)lights(60420,1080,0),\n[61500,4020](61500,330,0)And (61830,180,0)I'll (62010,150,0)be (62160,600,0)waiting (62760,180,0)in (62940,120,0)the 